<?php
return ['messages'=>['<p>1. What was EJI’s purpose behind the JGA 2025 booth concept?<br /><br />At <strong>JGA 2025</strong>, we chose to focus on <strong>purpose and people</strong> over showcasing our jewellery creations. Our goal was to highlight <strong>emerging talents</strong>, offering them a distinguished platform to share their creativity and engage directly with the industry. This initiative reflects our ongoing commitment to <strong>corporate social responsibility</strong>, <strong>innovation</strong>, and <strong>nurturing the next generation</strong> of jewellery professionals.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>2. Who were the student designers featured at the EJI booth?<br /><br />We proudly featured a group of talented <strong>jewellery design students</strong> from <strong>Hong Kong Design Institute (HKDI)</strong> and <strong>Young College – Pro-Act Jewellery</strong>. Each student brought their own unique style, story, and perspective, contributing to a total different yet very inspiring jewellery showcase around the show floor.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>3. How is EJI supporting young talent in the jewellery industry long-term?<br /><br />EJI is committed to <strong>empowering the next generation</strong> through meaningful exposure, and long-term opportunities. Beyond our initiative at JGA 2025, we continue to build bridges between generations by offering <strong>creative art workshops </strong>for children of various age groups. Our vision is to help shape a more inclusive, sustainable future for the industry.</p>'=>'<p>1. EJI 在 JGA 2025 展位背后的概念是什么？<br><br>在<strong> JGA 2025</strong>，我们选择聚焦于<strong>目标与人</strong>，而非展示我们的珠宝创作。目标是突出<strong>新一代人才</strong>，为他们提供一个卓越的平台分享创意并直接与行业互动。这一计划反映了我们对<strong>企业社会责任</strong>、<strong>创新</strong>及<strong>培育下一代</strong>珠宝专业人士的持续承诺。  </p>
<p> </p>
<p>2. EJI 展位上那些学生设计师是谁？<br><br>他们是来自<strong>香港设计学院（HKDI）</strong>与 <strong>Pro-Act 珠宝青年学院</strong>的一群才华横溢的<strong>珠宝设计学生</strong>。每位学生带来了独特的风格、故事和视角，为展会注入截然不同的元素 </p>
<p> </p>
<p>3. EJI 如何长期支持珠宝行业的年轻人才？<br><br>EJI 持续通过为不同年龄的儿童提供<strong>创意艺术工作坊</strong>，<strong>培育下一代</strong>。我们的愿景是塑造一个更具包容性、可持续的珠宝行业未来。  </p>','<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>Designed by</em> <strong>CHAN, Ying Sum</strong><br /></span></p><div><div><div><p>SHAPE - BA (Hons) Jewellery, Materials and Design <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI Jewellery</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/clearjewelry_sc/#">@clearjewelry_sc</a></strong></p></div></div>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>设计：</em> <strong>CHAN, Ying Sum</strong><br></span></p><div><div><div><p>SHAPE – 珠宝、材料与设计荣誉学士 <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/clearjewelry_sc/#">@clearjewelry_sc</a></strong></p></div></div>','<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>Designed by</em> <strong>NG, Chun Fan</strong><br /></span></p><div><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">Higher Diploma in Jewellery Design and Technology </span>|</span> HKDI Jewellery</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/frankie_jy/#">@frankie_jy</a></strong></p>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off fo