ne text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI Jewellery</p><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/sagitts.jewelry/#">@sagitts.jewelry</a></strong></p></div>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>设计：</em> <strong>YEUNG, Hoi Kiu Melody</strong><br></span></p><div><p>SHAPE – 珠宝、材料与设计荣誉学士 <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI</p><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/sagitts.jewelry/#">@sagitts.jewelry</a></strong></p></div>','<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>Designed by</em><strong> CHUNG, Ka Chun</strong><br /></span></p><div><div><div><div><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">Higher Diploma in Jewellery Design and Technology </span>|</span> HKDI Jewellery</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/jewellery_tinnnn/#">@jewellery_tinnnn</a></strong></p><p> </p></div></div></div>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>设计：</em><strong> CHUNG, Ka Chun</strong><br></span></p><div><div><div><div><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">珠宝设计与技术高级文凭 </span>|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/jewellery_tinnnn/#">@jewellery_tinnnn</a></strong></p><p> </p></div></div></div>','<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>Designed by <br /></em><strong>LEE, </strong></span><strong>Hoi Ying</strong>, <br /><strong>LAM, </strong><strong>Kwai Tung</strong>,<br /><strong>LEE, Wai Kiu</strong> &amp; <br /><strong>TONG, Wan Yiu</strong> </p><p>Pro-Act Jewellery <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"> | Young College</span></p><div> </div>'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>设计：<br></em><strong>LEE, </strong></span><strong>Hoi Ying</strong>, <br><strong>LAM, </strong><strong>Kwai Tung</strong>,<br><strong>LEE, Wai Kiu</strong> &amp; <br><strong>TONG, Wan Yiu</strong> </p><p>Pro-Act 珠寶<span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"> | 青年學院</span></p><div> </div>','<p>At EJI, social corporate responsibility is not a checklist – it’s our core value. As a responsible jewellery manufacturer, we are deeply committed to nurturing new talent, championing creativity, and building a dignified and sustainable future for the jewellery industry</p><p>Our initiative at JGA 2025 marks just the beginning of this journey. And we invite you to walk alongside us as we continue to empower, engage and build what comes next. Let’s shine together.</p>'=>'<p>对 EJI 而言，企业社会责任不是一份清单——它是我们的核心价值。作为负责任的珠宝制造商，我们致力于培育新人才、推广创意，为珠宝行业打造可持续未来。 </p><p>我们在 JGA 2025 的计划仅仅是这一旅程的开始。我们邀请您与我们同行，继续赋能、互动并共创未来，一起发光。  </p>','<p>At this year’s <a href="https://jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com/"><strong>Jewellery &amp; Gem Asia Hong Kong (JGA) 2025</strong></a>, we made a subtle yet significant shift. Not just our positioning on the show floor, but in our perspective.</p><p>We asked ourselves a simple but radical question: <br />“What if a trade fair booth wasn’t about showcasing what we’ve created – but what we believe in?”</p><p>So we set aside the traditional business approach to a B2B jewellery exhibition:<br />No commercials products.<br />No new launches.<br />No business agenda.</p><p>Instead, we embraced a bold idea: to hand over the spotlight to the <strong>next generation of talents</strong>, and to spark a conversation about the future of jewellery industry.</p><p>The result? A space that drew visitors to stop by our booth with surprise, curiosity, and engagement.</p>'=>'<p>今年的<a href="https://jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com/"><strong>六月香港珠宝首饰展览会（JGA 2025）</strong></a>，EJI 带来了微妙但意义深远的变革。 </p><p>我们问了自己一个简单却大胆的问题：<br>“如果珠宝展位展示的不是产品，而是我们的信念，会怎样？”</p><p>于是，EJI 摒弃了传统 B2B 珠宝展的商业模式：<br>没有商业产品。<br>没有新品发布。<br>没有会议流程。<br><br></p><p>取而代之，我们采取了一个创新做法：将聚光灯交给<strong>下一代人才</strong>。<br><br></p><p>结果，一个吸引访客驻足、充满惊喜、好奇和互动的空间应运而生。 </p>','<p>From the very beginning, we knew this would challenge expectations.<br /><br />Our space at JGA this year wasn’t built to attract buyers <br />– it was designed to spark genuine connection, and to shift the spotlight away from us, <br />toward something more meaningful.<br /><br />With the open layout and the oversized glowing letters of our name, the space felt different because it <strong><em>was</em></strong> different. <br /><br />It wasn’t a PR stunt. <br />We didn’t pitch a story. <br />We simply showed up with a purpose <br />– to express our belief in the future of the jewellery industry.</p>'=>'<p>从一开始我们就知道这个决定充满挑战。<br>这次的展位不是为吸引买家而设计——然而，它是一个促进连接的空间。<br>将焦点从我们身上，转移到更有意义的方向。<br>开放式布局、醒目发光的超大字母名称，形成了<strong><em>独特</em></strong>的空间。<br>这并非公关噱头。<br>没有推销故事，只有目标——表达我们对珠宝行业未来的信念。</p>','<p>To all who stopped by – to ask, to share, or just to listen – thank you. You made this space come alive. Your presence gave these students something powerful:</p><p>A sense of recognition and belonging in the industry.</p><p>And in return, they reminded us of all of what the jewellery can truly dbe: meaningful, inclusive, and full of potential.</p>'=>'<p>感谢所有驻足的人，无论是提问、分享，还是聆听，你们都让这个空间充满了生命力，给了学生们强大的支持——  </p><p>一种行业认可与归属感。</p><p>同时，学生们也提醒了我们珠宝真正的力量：充满意义与包容性，潜力无限。</p>','<p>We stepped back - to let them step forward.<br />And they did.</p>
<p>Not just with their stunning creations, but with their insights, their energy, their courage, and their dreams. They brought the real sparkle.</p>
<p>Over four days at JGA, what unfolded was far more powerful than we had imagined. It became a space where generations connected, where ideas were exchanged. The students soaked in the real business world experience, engaged with professionals, and – perhaps for the first time – felt what it means to belong in the jewellery industry.</p>
<p>Their sparkle wasn’t in gemstones. It was in imagination, courage, and vision.</p>'=>'<p>我们暂时退后——让他们大步前行。<br>而他们做到了。</p>
<p>那些耀眼的创作，承载了学生们的想法、能量、勇气和梦想；他们带来了真正的光芒。 </p>
<p>这4天的成果远超想象。我们的展位成为一个世代交汇、思想交流的空间。学生们有机会与专业人士互动，体验真实的商界，感受属于珠宝行业的归属感。  </p>
<p>他们的光芒源于想象力、勇气和远见；比宝石更耀眼。 </p>','A Different Kind of Presence'=>'与众不同的存在','A Quiet Shift Spoke Loudly'=>'全新面貌 重大变革','At the heart of this initiative was a group of passionate jewellery design students from Hong Kong Design Institution (HKDI) and Young College – Pro-Act Jewellery.'=>'这个计划的核心，是一群来自香港设计学院（HKDI）与 Pro-Act 珠宝青年学院、充满热情的珠宝设计学生。','Empower. Engage. Build the Future.'=>'赋能、互动、共创未来  ','Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)'=>'常见问题 (FAQ)','Letting the Next Generation Shine'=>'让下一代发光发热','Photo Credit: Informa Markets Hong Kong'=>'照片：Informa Markets Hong Kong','Thank you – For Making This Matter'=>'感谢每一位，让一切充满意义','The Stunning Jewellery Pieces'=>'令人惊艳的珠宝作品','Watch the Full Video'=>'观看视频','caption-image-ba8a09b'=>'照片：Informa Markets Hong Kong','dailymotion_url-video-29b49b8'=>'https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x6tqhqb','editor-text-editor-140bf9c'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>设计：</em> <strong>NG, Chun Fan</strong><br></span></p><div><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">珠宝设计与技术高级文凭 </span>|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/frankie_jy/#">@frankie_jy</a></strong></p>','editor-text-editor-21da0df'=>'<p>从一开始我们就知道这个决定充满挑战。<br>这次的展位不是为吸引买家而设计——然而，它是一个促进连接的空间。<br>将焦点从我们身上，转移到更有意义的方向。<br>开放式布局、醒目发光的超大字母名称，形成了<strong><em>独特</em></strong>的空间。<br>这并非公关噱头。<br>没有推销故事，只有目标——表达我们对珠宝行业未来的信念。</p>','editor-text-editor-398eaf2'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>设计：</em> <strong>SIU, Wing Ki</strong><br></span></p><div><p>SHAPE – 珠宝、材料与设计荣誉学士 <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/kakudo._.official/#">@kakudo._.official</a></strong></p>','editor-text-editor-4afa2ea'=>'<p>对 EJI 而言，企业社会责任不是一份清单——它是我们的核心价值。作为负责任的珠宝制造商，我们致力于培育新人才、推广创意，为珠宝行业打造可持续未来。 </p><p>我们在 JGA 2025 的计划仅仅是这一旅程的开始。我们邀请您与我们同行，继续赋能、互动并共创未来，一起发光。  </p>','editor-text-editor-5917c9e'=>'<p>感谢所有驻足的人，无论是提问、分享，还是聆听，你们都让这个空间充满了生命力，给了学生们强大的支持——  </p><p>一种行业认可与归属感。</p><p>同时，学生们也提醒了我们珠宝真正的力量：充满意义与包容性，潜力无限。</p>','editor-text-editor-83f3076'=>'<p>我们暂时退后——让他们大步前行。<br>而他们做到了。</p>
<p>那些耀眼的创作，承载了学生们的想法、能量、勇气和梦想；他们带来了真正的光芒。 </p>
<p>这4天的成果远超想象。我们的展位成为一个世代交汇、思想交流的空间。学生们有机会与专业人士互动，体验真实的商界，感受属于珠宝行业的归属感。  </p>
<p>他们的光芒源于想象力、勇气和远见；比宝石更耀眼。 </p>','editor-text-editor-9c060e7'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>设计：</em> <strong>CHAN, Ying Sum</strong><br></span></p><div><div><div><p>SHAPE – 珠宝、材料与设计荣誉学士 <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/clearjewelry_sc/#">@clearjewelry_sc</a></strong></p></div></div>','editor-text-editor-b685416'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>设计：<br></em><strong>LEE, </strong></span><strong>Hoi Ying</strong>, <br><strong>LAM, </strong><strong>Kwai Tung</strong>,<br><strong>LEE, Wai Kiu</strong> &amp; <br><strong>TONG, Wan Yiu</strong> </p><p>Pro-Act 珠寶<span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"> | 青年學院</span></p><div> </div>','editor-text-editor-bcdc4a6'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>设计：</em><strong> CHUNG, Ka Chun</strong><br></span></p><div><div><div><div><p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier"><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none">珠宝设计与技术高级文凭 </span>|</span> HKDI</p></div><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/jewellery_tinnnn/#">@jewellery_tinnnn</a></strong></p><p> </p></div></div></div>','editor-text-editor-cddbd8e'=>'<p>今年的<a href="https://jga.exhibitions.jewellerynet.com/"><strong>六月香港珠宝首饰展览会（JGA 2025）</strong></a>，EJI 带来了微妙但意义深远的变革。 </p><p>我们问了自己一个简单却大胆的问题：<br>“如果珠宝展位展示的不是产品，而是我们的信念，会怎样？”</p><p>于是，EJI 摒弃了传统 B2B 珠宝展的商业模式：<br>没有商业产品。<br>没有新品发布。<br>没有会议流程。<br><br></p><p>取而代之，我们采取了一个创新做法：将聚光灯交给<strong>下一代人才</strong>。<br><br></p><p>结果，一个吸引访客驻足、充满惊喜、好奇和互动的空间应运而生。 </p>','editor-text-editor-e1790af'=>'<p><span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none"><em>设计：</em> <strong>YEUNG, Hoi Kiu Melody</strong><br></span></p><div><p>SHAPE – 珠宝、材料与设计荣誉学士 <span class="OYPEnA font-feature-liga-off font-feature-clig-off font-feature-calt-off text-decoration-none text-strikethrough-none font-size-modifier">|</span> HKDI</p><p>Instagram <strong><a href="https://www.instagram.com/sagitts.jewelry/#">@sagitts.jewelry</a></strong></p></div>','editor-text-editor-f52df4a'=>'<p>1. EJI 在 JGA 2025 展位背后的概念是什么？<br><br>在<strong> JGA 2025</strong>，我们选择聚焦于<strong>目标与人</strong>，而非展示我们的珠宝创作。目标是突出<strong>新一代人才</strong>，为他们提供一个卓越的平台分享创意并直接与行业互动。这一计划反映了我们对<strong>企业社会责任</strong>、<strong>创新</strong>及<strong>培育下一代</strong>珠宝专业人士的持续承诺。  </p>
<p> </p>
<p>2. EJI 展位上那些学生设计师是谁？<br><br>他们是来自<strong>香港设计学院（HKDI）</strong>与 <strong>Pro-Act 珠宝青年学院</strong>的一群才华横溢的<strong>珠宝设计学生</strong>。每位学生带来了独特的风格、故事和视角，为展会注入截然不同的元素 </p>
<p> </p>
<p>3. EJI 如何长期支持珠宝行业的年轻人才？<br><br>EJI 持续通过为不同年龄的儿童提供<strong>创意艺术工作坊</strong>，<strong>培育下一代</strong>。我们的愿景是塑造一个更具包容性、可持续的珠宝行业未来。  </p>','https://hkdi.edu.hk/EN'=>'https://hkdi.edu.hk/EN','https://vimeo.com/235215203'=>'https://vimeo.com/235215203','https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x6tqhqb'=>'https://www.dailymotion.com/video/x6tqhqb','https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cjkMC-KsVu4'=>'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cjkMC-KsVu4','nested-tabs-tab_title-01e70b3-9b0ef20'=>'观看视频','title-heading-29bb38b'=>'这个计划的核心，是一群来自香港设计学院（HKDI）与 Pro-Act 珠宝青年学院、充满热情的珠宝设计学生。','title-heading-3cef6fe'=>'感谢每一位，让一切充满意义','title-heading-4c9386f'=>'与众不同的存在','title-heading-8de0a78'=>'令人惊艳的珠宝作品','title-heading-8df1078'=>'全新面貌 重大变革','title-heading-bfe2ee9'=>'让下一代发光发热','title-heading-c70e70b'=>'常见问题 (FAQ)','title-heading-ec35217'=>'赋能、互动、共创未来  ','url-heading-29bb38b'=>'https://hkdi.edu.hk/EN','vimeo_url-video-29b49b8'=>'https://vimeo.com/235215203','youtube_url-video-29b49b8'=>'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cjkMC-KsVu4']];
